<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/586425-why-read-this-text-this-is-an-edited">Why read this text? This is an edited version. The more complete text is called &#39;The Autumn of the Middle Ages.&#39; &#39;Waning&#39; leaves out too many of the comical anecdotes.</a>
</div>
